Uses of Package
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers

  • Packages that use org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers 
    Package Description
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis
    This is the top-level package for the AGCL plug-in.
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.config
    This package contains definitions to manage the plugin's preferences.
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.results
    This package contains classes to manage analysis results.
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers
    This package contains the main verification framework that links the algorithms from the org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.algorithms package to an external (PSL) verifier.
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.impl  
    org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.util
